<headline>Special Weather Statement issued February 22 at 7:48PM EST  by NWS Detroit</headline>
<description>...POTENTIAL FOR SLICK CONDITIONS LATE THIS EVENING...
WEATHER...
*  Pockets of light freezing rain and drizzle will continue to
lift across the area late this evening, as temperatures hover
at or just below freezing.
* Light ice accumulations are possible on untreated area roadways
and surfaces.
IMPACTS...
* Light icing will lead to hazardous conditions on untreated
roads and walking surfaces.
&amp;&amp;
PRECAUTIONARY/PREPAREDNESS ACTIONS...
* Motorists are urged to use caution and account for hazardous
driving conditions by slowing down and allowing extra time.
* Prepare, plan and stay informed. Visit http://go.usa.gov/c7kkP</description>
